Purpose: Collect essential farmer information

Layout:
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [<]      Your Profile           |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   Step 2 of 5                    |
|   [========-----------]          |
|                                  |
|   [Camera icon - Add Photo]      |  <- Optional
|                                  |
|   Your Name                      |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | Jean-Pierre Dubois         | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   Farm Name                      |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | Ferme des Trois Chenes     | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   Country                        |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | France                  [v]| |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   Region                         |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | Aube                    [v]| |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|   [====== Continue ======]       |
+----------------------------------+
```

Components:
- Photo picker: 80x80px circle, optional, camera icon
- Text inputs: 56px height, 16sp text
- Dropdowns: 56px height, searchable

Validation:
- Name: Required, 2-50 characters
- Farm name: Required, 2-100 characters
- Country: Required, from supported list
- Region: Required after country selected

Data Persistence:
- Save locally on each field blur
- Resume if app closes mid-onboarding

