Screen 1.4: Bank Details

Purpose: Set up payout destination

Layout:
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [<]      Bank Details           |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   Step 3 of 5                    |
|   [============-------]          |
|                                  |
|   "Where should we send          |
|    your earnings?"               |
|                                  |
|   [i] Your bank details are      |
|       encrypted and secure.      |
|                                  |
|   Account Holder Name            |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | Jean-Pierre Dubois         | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   IBAN                           |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | FR76 3000 4000 0500 0000   | |
|   | 1234 567                    | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   BIC/SWIFT (optional)           |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | BNPAFRPP                   | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|   [====== Continue ======]       |
|                                  |
|   "Add bank details later"       |
+----------------------------------+
```

Components:
- Info banner: Light blue background, lock icon
- IBAN input: Auto-format with spaces, uppercase
- Validation: Real-time IBAN checksum validation

Validation:
- IBAN: Valid format and checksum for country
- BIC: Valid format if provided
- Allow skip: Can add later in Settings

Security:
- Data encrypted in transit and at rest
- Masked display after entry (FR76    4567)

