Screen 1.5: Plot Registration

Purpose: Add first hemp plot

Layout:
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [<]      Add Your Plot          |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   Step 4 of 5                    |
|   [================---]          |
|                                  |
|   "Tell us about your            |
|    hemp plot"                    |
|                                  |
|   Plot Name                      |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | Parcelle Nord              | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   Size (hectares)                |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | [-]     12.5         [+]  | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   Location                       |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | [Pin] Tap to set on map   | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   [====== Map View ======]       |
|   | [Satellite map imagery]    | |
|   | [Draggable pin in center]  | |
|   |                            | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|   [====== Continue ======]       |
+----------------------------------+
```

Map Interaction:
```
+----------------------------------+
|         Set Plot Location        |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   [=============================]|
|   [=    SATELLITE MAP         =]|
|   [=                          =]|
|   [=         [X]              =]|  <- Draggable pin
|   [=       Current            =]|
|   [=                          =]|
|   [=                          =]|
|   [=============================]|
|                                  |
|   48.2847deg N, 4.0772deg E      |
|                                  |
|   [ Use Current Location ]       |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|   [====== Confirm Location =====]|
+----------------------------------+
```

Components:
- Size stepper: +/- buttons, 0.5 ha increments, manual entry
- Map: Satellite imagery, draggable pin, zoom controls
- Location button: GPS permission request

Validation:
- Plot name: Required, unique per farmer
- Size: 0.5 - 500 hectares
- Location: Required, valid coordinates

