Screen 1.6: Planting Dates

Purpose: Capture planting and harvest timing

Layout:
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [<]     Planting Dates          |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   Step 4 of 5 (continued)        |
|   [================---]          |
|                                  |
|   "When did you plant            |
|    this plot?"                   |
|                                  |
|   Planting Date                  |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | [Cal] 15 April 2026        | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   Expected Harvest               |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | [Cal] 15 September 2026    | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   Hemp Variety (optional)        |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | Fedora 17               [v]| |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   [i] Carbon capture is measured |
|       from planting to harvest.  |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|   [====== Continue ======]       |
+----------------------------------+
```

Components:
- Date pickers: Native date picker, calendar icon
- Variety dropdown: Common varieties + "Other"
- Info box: Explains why dates matter

Validation:
- Planting date: Past or today
- Harvest date: After planting, within 8 months
- Auto-calculate expected carbon based on dates

