Screen 1.7: Sensor Pairing

Purpose: Connect IoT sensor to plot

Layout (Initial):
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [<]      Connect Sensor         |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   Step 5 of 5                    |
|   [====================]         |
|                                  |
|   [Illustration: Phone           |
|    near sensor device]           |
|                                  |
|   "Hold your phone near          |
|    the sensor"                   |
|                                  |
|   The sensor is the small        |
|   device installed in your       |
|   field.                         |
|                                  |
|   [Pulse animation: Searching]   |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|   "Can't find sensor?"           |
|   [ Enter code manually ]        |
+----------------------------------+
```

Layout (Manual Entry):
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [<]      Enter Sensor Code      |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   "Find the code on the          |
|    back of your sensor"          |
|                                  |
|   [Illustration: Sensor back     |
|    with code location]           |
|                                  |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | GHL-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX         | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|   [====== Connect ======]        |
+----------------------------------+
```

Layout (Success):
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [<]      Sensor Connected       |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|                                  |
|         [Checkmark Circle]       |
|              Green               |
|                                  |
|   "Sensor connected!"            |
|                                  |
|   Sensor ID: GHL-2847-AXBK       |
|   Signal: Strong                 |
|   Battery: 100%                  |
|                                  |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|   [====== Continue ======]       |
+----------------------------------+
```

Components:
- NFC detection: Automatic when screen active
- Manual input: 16-character code with dashes
- Success animation: Checkmark with confetti

Interactions:
- NFC tap -> Auto-detect and pair
- Manual entry -> Validate code format
- Success -> Vibrate, show confirmation

Error Handling:
- NFC not available: Skip directly to manual
- Invalid code: "Code not recognized. Check and try again."
- Sensor already paired: "This sensor is already registered to another plot."

