5.2 Main App Screens

Screen 2.1: Home Dashboard

Purpose: At-a-glance status of earnings and plots

Layout:
```
+----------------------------------+
|   [Logo]    Good morning,    [Bell]
|             Jean-Pierre          |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | EARNINGS THIS SEASON       | |
|   |                            | |
|   |     EUR 1,247.50           | |  <- Large, bold
|   |                            | |
|   |  +EUR 85.20 this week      | |  <- Smaller, green
|   |                            | |
|   |  [View Details ->]         | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   YOUR PLOTS                     |
|                                  |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | [=] Parcelle Nord   [Grn]  | |
|   |     12.5 ha                | |
|   |     8.2 tonnes CO2         | |
|   |     Updated 2h ago    [->] | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | [=] Parcelle Sud    [Ylw]  | |
|   |     8.0 ha                 | |
|   |     5.1 tonnes CO2         | |
|   |     Updated 2h ago    [->] | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
|   [ + Add Another Plot ]         |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
|  [Home]  [Plots]  [EUR]  [Gear] |
+----------------------------------+
```

Components:

Earnings Card:
- Background: Gradient green
- Main amount: 32sp, bold, white
- Weekly change: 16sp, lighter green background
- Tap area: Entire card navigates to Earnings

Plot Cards:
- Status indicator: Colored circle (green/yellow/red)
- Plot name: 18sp, bold
- Size and carbon: 14sp, secondary color
- Last update: 12sp, tertiary color
- Arrow: Navigation affordance

Status Colors:
- Green: All systems normal
- Yellow: Attention needed (sensor weak, verification pending)
- Red: Action required (sensor offline, issue detected)

Pull-to-Refresh:
- Pull down to sync latest data
- Show "Last updated: X minutes ago" after refresh

