Progress Bar:
- Horizontal, filled based on completion
- Shows absolute and percentage
- Tap to see detailed breakdown

Sensor Gauges:
- Horizontal bar visualization
- Color-coded (green = good range)
- Last reading timestamp

Activity Timeline:
- Reverse chronological
- Icon indicates type (check, money, alert)
- Collapsible to last 3 items

