5.3 Alert & Error Screens

Screen 3.1: Sensor Offline Alert

Purpose: Guide farmer through sensor troubleshooting

Layout:
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [X]     Sensor Alert            |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|         [Warning Icon]           |
|           Yellow                 |
|                                  |
|   "Sensor offline"               |
|                                  |
|   Parcelle Nord sensor           |
|   hasn't reported in 24 hours.   |
|                                  |
|   TRY THESE STEPS:               |
|                                  |
|   [1] Check battery              |
|       The sensor uses 2 AA       |
|       batteries. Replace if      |
|       needed.                    |
|                                  |
|   [2] Check for damage           |
|       Make sure sensor hasn't    |
|       been knocked over or       |
|       damaged.                   |
|                                  |
|   [3] Move phone closer          |
|       Try reconnecting from      |
|       within 2 meters.           |
|                                  |
|   [ Try Reconnecting ]           |
|                                  |
|   [Still not working? Contact    |
|    Support]                      |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
```

Components:
- Warning icon: Yellow/amber
- Numbered steps: Clear troubleshooting
- Action buttons: Try fix, escalate to support

---

Screen 3.2: Offline Mode Banner

Purpose: Indicate offline state, ensure farmer knows data may be stale

Layout:
```
+----------------------------------+
|  [!] You're offline              |
|      Last updated 2 hours ago    |
+----------------------------------+
|                                  |
|   [Regular dashboard content     |
|    with slightly muted colors]   |
|                                  |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|   | [!] Some actions are       | |
|   | unavailable offline.       | |
|   | They'll complete when you  | |
|   | reconnect.                 | |
|   +----------------------------+ |
|                                  |
+----------------------------------+
```

Components:
- Sticky banner: Persists at top
- Muted UI: Slight opacity reduction
- Info card: Explains limitations

Offline Capabilities:
- View cached dashboard data
- View cached earnings history
- View plot details (last cached)
- Queue: Report issue (sends when online)

Offline Limitations:
- Cannot add new plot
- Cannot pair new sensor
- Cannot change bank details
- Data may be stale

