6. User Flows

6.1 First-Time Onboarding Flow

```
[Install App]
     |
     v
[Welcome Screen]
     |
     v
[Phone Verification] --fail--> [Retry / Support]
     |
     | success
     v
[Farmer Profile]
     |
     v
[Bank Details] --skip--> [Plot Registration]
     |                          |
     | filled                   |
     v                          |
[Plot Registration] <-----------+
     |
     v
[Planting Dates]
     |
     v
[Sensor Pairing] --no sensor--> [Skip / Contact Support]
     |                                   |
     | paired                            |
     v                                   |
[Setup Complete] <-----------------------+
     |
     v
[Home Dashboard]
```

Time to Complete: 5-8 minutes

---

6.2 Check Earnings Flow

```
[Home Dashboard]
     |
     | tap earnings card
     v
[Earnings Screen]
     |
     | tap transaction
     v
[Transaction Detail]
     |
     | tap download receipt
     v
[PDF Generated / Share Sheet]
```

Taps Required: 2-3

---

6.3 Respond to Sensor Alert Flow

```
[Push Notification: Sensor Offline]
     |
     | tap notification
     v
[Sensor Alert Screen]
     |
     | follow troubleshooting
     v
[Try Reconnecting]
     |
     +--success---> [Success Message] --> [Plot Detail]
     |
     +--fail---> [Contact Support Option]
                       |
                       v
                 [Support Chat / Call]
```

Target Resolution: < 5 minutes self-service

---

6.4 Add New Plot Flow

```
[Home Dashboard]
     |
     | tap "Add Plot"
     v
[Plot Registration]
     |
     v
[Planting Dates]
     |
     v
[Sensor Pairing] --no sensor yet--> [Request Sensor]
     |                                     |
     | paired                              |
     v                                     v
[Confirmation] <---sensor arrives--- [Awaiting Sensor]
     |
     v
[Home Dashboard with New Plot]
```

---

6.5 View Verification Status Flow

```
[Plot Detail]
     |
     | tap verification section
     v
[Verification Status]
     |
     | tap previous verification
     v
[Verification Detail]
     |
     | shows: dates, data sources,
     | tonnes verified, earnings
```

