Background:       #FFFFFF  (rgb: 255, 255, 255)
Surface:          #F5F5F5  (rgb: 245, 245, 245)
Divider:          #E0E0E0  (rgb: 224, 224, 224)
```

C. Typography Scale

```
Display:      32sp / Bold    - Main earnings amount
Headline:     24sp / Bold    - Screen titles
Title:        20sp / Medium  - Section headers
Body Large:   18sp / Regular - Plot names, emphasis
Body:         16sp / Regular - Primary content
Body Small:   14sp / Regular - Secondary content
Caption:      12sp / Regular - Timestamps, labels
```

